It seemed too quick for Finch at 146.9km/h, the ball skidding on to him and hitting him on the helmet before he was halfway into his pull. The ball hits him flush on the peak. commentary: Faheem Ashraf to Maxwell, OUT direct hit, and Maxwell walks off straight away, even as the umpire sends it upstairs. He pushed to mid off and set off for what would have been a tight single, had the throw not been deadly accurate to find him short. He just hit it and set off, but Haris Sohail's throw was sharp and on target. Replays simply confirm his demise
